      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 14,
      "message": "We have to perform a destination port translation for all packets with destination of NEXUS3 IP address. Thus I would suggest:\n\n1) rename NODE_IP to NEXUS3_IP to make it obvious\n\n2) store NEXUS3 IP address instead of local NODE IP, e.g. by:\nhost nexus3.onap.org | awk '/has address/ { print $4 ; exit }'",
